## Description {#details}

This class represents a memory mapped file.

It is based on boost::iostreams::mapped&#95;file.

Definition at line 1262 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/filesystem-h">FileSystem.h</a>.
